{"title":"小红帽脱险记  ９","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记  ９"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚，明晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚虽还没有到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽可已经忍不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得不得了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗在啃骨头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马在吃青草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜蜂在等着鲜花吸花汁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不会管我小红帽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是多么穷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿不出骨头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有土地长青草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有花园种鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁肯不要老山妖的好东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白白的来帮助我，抵抗他？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我虽然年纪小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我已经知到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上再也找不到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肯牺牲自己为别人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的人实在少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"实在少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少到没有了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚，今晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是再也逃不掉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那漆黑的魔手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那血盆的大口！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越想越害怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越害怕越没有办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他赶快躲到屋角里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面哭一面想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面想一面流眼泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉钉钉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铛铛铛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打铁，补锅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钉钉钉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铛铛铛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打铁，补锅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个小铁匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑着风箱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正从茅屋边走过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他被煤烟薰得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象个小黑人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只露出光闪闪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两双亮眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽从门缝偷偷的向外看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁匠正走到了茅屋前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽看到了他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓得只是打寒颤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这下可真完了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖已经派来了一个小山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是再也逃不掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再也逃不掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听见了门里面有哭声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他放下了风箱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻敲着破柴门："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“里面是哪个小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么哭哭啼啼的？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果是迷了路的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我可以送他回家去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果是贪玩逃学的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我可没有功夫管他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果是吵吃吵玩不肯工作的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那我小铁匠可还要打他！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呵，原来是你呀，小铁匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你不要打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你不要打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不是迷了路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不是逃学不上课，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不是吵吃吵玩不肯工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是害怕那老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说他今晚一定来吃我。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我还这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃掉了就不能长得高高的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一棵树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃掉了就不能长得壮壮的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一条牛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我还这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还没有本事到田里去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种出麦子做馍馍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种出大米来蒸糕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我还这么小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还没有本事到山上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斫大树，盖房子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挖石头，造大桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“说到造大桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小铁匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有一个大秘密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你愿听不愿听？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要赌一个咒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准笑我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不准告诉人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“行！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我赌咒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果我告诉人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打铁的时候火烧我的眼睛。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我做过一个梦："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我造了一座桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象半天上的彩虹那么美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么长来那么高！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥上面走着黑头发的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红头发的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄头发的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灰头发的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们手牵着手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面唱又一面笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（未完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}